  "877010": {
    "name": "Beyond Contact",
    "steam_appid": 877010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Beyond Contact 是一款创新的科幻生存游戏，它采用自上而下的艺术风格，灵感源自于低俗科幻漫画，带来一种独特的视觉美感。<br><br>玩家可以选择参与以叙事为主线的故事模式或开放的征服模式，Beyond Contact 的叙事目标和道德困境会让人不禁想起当代科幻电影。<br><br>Beyond Contact 的玩法包括一个强大的研究和制作系统，让玩家能够创造各种各样的工具、武器、小玩意和结构，帮助自己生存下来。栖息地的建设、耕种和游戏机制都非常有趣，使用起来也令人满意。游戏的开放世界有着各种各样的动物和植物。对于那些喜欢休闲节奏的玩家，游戏推出了一系列的游戏定制设置。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/275da830649fd051087bd760e35db757.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/275da830649fd051087bd760e35db757.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/275da830649fd051087bd760e35db757.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的冒险立刻开始！</h2>2766年，星联负责探险的太空军的精英成员奎因·希克斯奉命回应在已知星域边缘愈演愈烈的一场危机。基特恩星正在崩溃。来自星球内部的不明能量源正威胁着星球上的文明……<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/03bf056387aeff771c9169a60a23f2f1.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/03bf056387aeff771c9169a60a23f2f1.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/03bf056387aeff771c9169a60a23f2f1.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >征服模式</h2>在 Beyond Contact 全新征服模式中，加入对基特恩星控制权的争夺。这种不受拘束的生存体验带来了无尽的玩法，更多基地建设的机会，并可对强大的腐化部落发起史诗般的战斗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事模式</h2>通过与专门社区的合作，故事模式将让玩家沉浸在史诗般的探索和发现之旅中，而你将为拯救整个文明、避免星球毁灭而战斗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作模式</h2>与其他玩家合作，大家共同进退。每位玩家都能选择一个具有独特能力、技能和工具的角色。利用新的多人游戏功能让倒下的队友复活。合作完成共同的研究和目标。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/08ad32a632015b8eb3574e874ccb0c45.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/08ad32a632015b8eb3574e874ccb0c45.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/08ad32a632015b8eb3574e874ccb0c45.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态3D引擎</h2>基特恩星环境动态多样，细节丰富，且杀机四伏，你能在这里活下来吗？ <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/bd3cb2b277d0ad6991c644aa85abdb60.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/bd3cb2b277d0ad6991c644aa85abdb60.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/bd3cb2b277d0ad6991c644aa85abdb60.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >科幻风格背景 </h2>运用你的太空军制式装备、武器和环境防护服探索丰富多彩的异星环境，发现奇异的动植物，最终与基特恩星的古代文明对话。<br><br>现在推出各种独一无二的角色，而每个角色都有自己的技能、能力和装备。奎因是一位多面手，坎加是一位勇猛的战士，扎因教授是一位建筑专家。第 4 个角色正在开发中，将在发布后再加入。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/4e95a930f3492381288c0bea4f6e2498.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/4e95a930f3492381288c0bea4f6e2498.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/4e95a930f3492381288c0bea4f6e2498.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内容丰富的研究和制作</h2>扫描、收集、开采并回收这颗星球上奇特的原料，并运用富有深度的研究和制作系统获得收益，在这颗濒死星球上对抗往往对你抱有敌意的居民，并努力活下去。<br><br>利用新的农业系统和结构来创造转基因植物，在保护性栖息地内建立农场，优化产出，以确保你能在无情的世界中生存下去。   <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/372f67abb793597e1478114062ba3ddf.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/372f67abb793597e1478114062ba3ddf.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/372f67abb793597e1478114062ba3ddf.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直观的基地建设以及电网系统</h2>建造、扩张并保卫你的行动基地，同时最大化利用独特的电网和氧气/热能系统。<br><br>通过全新的栖息地系统，你可以建立最终的生存避难所，并将自己的基地建设创造力提升到新的水平。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/bc837f56ce2969a6f83fac051e2f3cd1.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/bc837f56ce2969a6f83fac051e2f3cd1.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/bc837f56ce2969a6f83fac051e2f3cd1.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情驱动的任务，以及不同阵营的外星NPC</h2>在旅途中帮助当地居民，与外星文明合作，探索原本未知的技术，并发现这颗星球濒死的真相。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/e8f94a77828bdc898d7bec9070c72711.poster.avif?t=1726630742\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/e8f94a77828bdc898d7bec9070c72711.webm?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/877010/extras/e8f94a77828bdc898d7bec9070c72711.mp4?t=1726630742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >衰亡的世界</h2>基特恩星曾经是一个欣欣向荣的世界，但现在被黑暗裂隙撕裂，变成了一个环境灾害和恶劣天气肆虐的星球。你能活下来吗？",
